high_descs: Walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the furthest spray bottle off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the tub, then turn left and walk over to the wall and look down.
Put the white spray bottle in the small silver bin that's on the ground.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the spray bottle off of the counter.
Turn around and walk toward the tub, then hang a left and walk up to the wall and look down.
Put the spray bottle in the small silver bin on the ground.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles into a small silver bin.

high_descs: Move forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Pick up the spray bottle on the counter, closest to the wall.
Turn around and step forward, then turn left to face the trash bin.
Put the spray bottle in the trash bin.
Turn around and move forward, then turn right to return to the counter adjacent to the sink.
Pick up the spray bottle on the counter.
Turn around and step forward, then turn left to face the trash bin.
Put the spray bottle in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles in the trash.

high_descs: Go forward, before reaching the shower turn left, go forward to the right side of the sink.
Take the white spray bottle closest to the candle on the counter.
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the towel on the wall.
Put the bottle in the metal bin below the towel.
Turn around, go forward past the shower, turn right, go forward to the right side of the sink.
Take the white spray bottle from the counter.
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the towel on the wall.
Put the bottle in the metal bin below the towel.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles in a metal bin.
